// - Basic history of bolo,
// - Basic history of CUORE

- Among many 0vbb experiments, CUORE uses somewhat unique technique that aims to reach ton-scale while also having high-resolution,
- Made possible by bolometric method with use of 130Te.
- It is a result of decades long saga of bolometric experiments searching for 0#nbb, that solved many engineering challenges along the way, with incremental improvements in lowering background radiation, noise reduction etc
  - Is housed in LNGSi, under ~ a kilometer of rock which is considered the largest deep underground laboratory facility of the world.


